snippet.title: Ace Attorney Investigations Collection - Allies & Adversaries Trailer
snippet.description:
Eager to jump into Edgeworth's shoes? The demo for Ace Attorney Investigations Collection is now available to download on Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 4, Xbox One, Windows, and Steam!

Official Website:
https://www.ace-attorney.com/investigations1-2/

Release Date: September 6, 2024
